nd\",\n        \"rationale\": \"With only 2 stocks meeting criteria (vs codex finding 5), need to verify the semiconductor filtering and MACD calculation are not too restrictive.\",\n        \"approach\": \"Review the semiconductor keyword filtering to ensure it's not missing relevant stocks, and verify MACD parameters (12, 26, 9) are correctly applied.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"change\": \"Address data source reliability\",\n        \"rationale\": \"Using simulated data undermines result validity. Need real market data or explicit acknowledgment that results are demonstrative only.\",\n        \"approach\": \"Either fix the akshare connectivity issue, use an alternative data source, or clearly document that results are for demonstration purposes and cannot be validated.\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
